com.javaweb

Interface Const


  • public interface Const
    Const.java

    It is interface for constant values for the game. Here are a lot of Strings, which we will put in external file later. It is made for internationalization. Also here are some integer values to reduce hardcoding.

    Version:
    1.0 29 Oct 2016
    Author:
    Andrii Chernysh {itcherry97@gmail.com}
